title: pyo3 crashes with ICE in gcc
body:
### Reproducing

```
git clone https://github.com/pyo3/pyo3
cd pyo3
git checkout c9d9e80acb56ba9faa9c401a0261dfee9385081c # Recent, but fixed commit
cargo test
```
